title: Sheena Queen of the Jungle Fiction House 1938 COMPLETE
description:
Ah yes, more good girl type comics from the golden age.  This time the ultimate in cheesecake; Sheena! Queen of the Jungle.  Many of you may know  her mainly from that Movie with Tanya Roberts (also in Beastmaster, and even played Midge in that 70's Show, a personal favorite of mine!) But this iswhere sheen all began:

First Origin
 
Sheena the was a child of explorer Cardwell Rivington. However, her father was killed accidentally by a native witch doctor named Koba. Koba then raises Sheena as his own daughter because he feels its his duty. Once grown, she becomes queen of the tribe and meets Bob Reynolds whom she chooses as her mate.


Second Origin 

In her second origin, Sheena was an orphan of missionaries. Bob was called Rick Thorne and Koba's role was fulfilled by a female witch named N'bid Ela.


Golden Age Appearances  

Jumbo Comics #1-167
Sheena, Queen of the Jungle #1-18
3-D Sheena, Jungle Queen

Seed for all to enjoy!  Sharing is caring!
